snippet.title: Z-Collapse - Release announcement
snippet.description:
Check out the announcement trailer for Z-Collapse, the upcoming grand-strategy game that simulates a global zombie invasion.

In Z-Collapse, select your country and try to make it survive. Undeads, bandits, other nations, many challenges await you. Avoid collapse at all costs.

Wishlist us now on Steam
